rows.label: qst100301_msg0002
rows.name: No! Pupun not okay at all!

rows.label: qst100301_msg0003
rows.name:
Pupun was just about to complete 40
hours of flight training and get license
for flying as much as Pupun want!

rows.label: qst100301_msg0004
rows.name:
Pupun always dream of zipping about
Alst skies, eating delicious treats of
every place, but...

rows.label: qst100301_msg0006
rows.name: Pupun have little problem right now.

rows.label: qst100301_msg0007
rows.name:
Nagging hunger in Pupun's stomach
very distracting.

rows.label: qst100301_msg0008
rows.name:
So hungry... Must eat... Must eat
something...

rows.label: qst100301_msg0501
rows.name:
Thank you from bottom of stomach.
But Pupun not quite full...

rows.label: qst100301_msg0502
rows.name:
Any more food, bring here, Pupun can
eat.
